==English==
{{wikipedia|Lex programming tool}}

===Etymology===
From ''[[lexical analysis]]'', from ''[[lexical]]''

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|lɛks}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛks|-ɛks]]

===Noun===
'''lex'''
#{{computing}} A program (originally developed under [[Unix]]) involved in [[lexical analysis]] -- specifically, a program for generating [[lexical analyzer]]s.

===Verb===
'''lex'''
#{{computing}} To lexically analyze a computer program's source code, prior to [[parse|parsing]] it.


